THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE ACKNOWLEDGMENTS

This project incorporates and builds upon the following third-party software:

OpenAI Whisper
Copyright (c) 2022 OpenAI
Licensed under the MIT License
https://github.com/openai/whisper

This software uses OpenAI's Whisper automatic speech recognition system as its
core transcription engine. Whisper is a neural net that approaches human level
robustness and accuracy on English speech recognition.

Citation for Whisper:
Radford, A., Kim, J. W., Xu, T., Brockman, G., McLeavey, C., & Sutskever, I. (2022).
Robust Speech Recognition via Large-Scale Weak Supervision. arXiv preprint arXiv:2212.04356.

PyTorch
